refactor: split monolithic create.ts into focused modules

- create.ts (804 lines) split into 7 files, all under 200 lines
- mock-app.ts: Obsidian App/Editor mock implementation
- extensions.ts: CM6 extension assembly
- link-handler.ts: link click handling
- expand-text.ts: Chinese bracket auto-conversion
- suggest.ts: autocomplete popup logic
- globals.d.ts: Window type declarations

Additional changes:
- Demo page converted from vanilla JS to Vue (App.vue + main.ts)
- Sample doc extracted to demo-doc.md (imported via ?raw)
- Added library build config (tsconfig.build.json → out/)
- Added vue and @vitejs/plugin-vue dependencies

Version: 1.0.0 → 1.1.0
